# ─── compiled artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────
src/target/
bin/lazar

# ─── runtime state (per-user, generated by lazar at runtime) ────────
# These directories live alongside src/ inside ~/lazar/ but are
# NEVER part of the published repo. They're populated by `--reset-all`
# from src/seed-skills/ and src/seed-hooks/, then evolve as the user
# runs the agent.
skills/
hooks/
memory/
workspace/
logs/

# ─── editor / IDE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── OS cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ─── secrets / local env ────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
*.local

# Note on Cargo.lock:
# We DO commit src/Cargo.lock — lazar is a binary, not a library, and
# locking dependency versions makes reproducible builds across machines.
